    -- Let B_fB be the subset defined by the forward map on f_B
    -- B_fB = {a ∈ A | f_B a = 1}
    -- But f_B a = if a ∈ B then 1 else 0
    -- So f_B a = 1 iff a ∈ B
    -- Thus, B_fB = B
    ext B
    simp
    <;> aesop
```

Finally, we complete the proof:

